data.description: Welcome to Cedar Grove at the Woodlands! This is a Cedar model, built in 2022 and is located on a beautiful lake view lot. This 3 bed, 2 bath home features upgraded Kitchen Aid stainless steel appliances, tile backsplash, quartz countertops, granite kitchen sink and upgraded cabinets with soft close doors and drawers in both the kitchen and both bathrooms. This home also features luxury vinyl plank floors, 8-foot doors throughout, and epoxy garage floor. HOA includes all landscaping as well as access to the heated resort style community pool, basketball court, playground and grills.
